'''手機連結'''是[[微软|微软]]为[[Windows_10|Windows 10]]开发的一款應用程式，用于连接[[Android|Android]]设备和Windows 10设备。用戶可以通過此應用程式直接在[[Windows|Windows]] [[个人电脑|PC]]上查看手机屏幕畫面、手機中2000张最新照片、发送[[簡訊|短信]]和拨打电话。该应用还具有跨设备复制和粘贴功能，例如用戶在Android設備上複製文本和图像，可在Windows设备上直接粘貼，反之亦然 <ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.onmsft.com/news/windows-10s-new-your-phone-app-lets-you-access-phone-texts-photos|title=Windows 10's new Your Phone app lets you access phone texts & photos|date=2018-10-03|work=On MSFT|accessdate=2018-10-19|language=en|archive-date=2022-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220107081040/https://www.onmsft.com/news/windows-10s-new-your-phone-app-lets-you-access-phone-texts-photos}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Microsoft begins testing phone screen mirroring with the Your Phone app|url=https://www.windowscentral.com/microsoft-starts-testing-phone-screen-mirroring-your-phone-windows-10-19h1|accessdate=2019-07-26|date=2019-03-12|work=Windows Central|language=en|archive-date=2022-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220107081025/https://www.windowscentral.com/microsoft-starts-testing-phone-screen-mirroring-your-phone-windows-10-19h1}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Galaxy Z Flip and S20 to get cross-platform copy and paste via Microsoft's Your Phone|url=https://www.androidpolice.com/2020/02/18/microsoft-your-phone-cross-device-copy-paste/|accessdate=2020-03-03|date=2020-02-18|work=Android Police|language=en-US|archive-date=2022-06-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220602061152/https://www.androidpolice.com/2020/02/18/microsoft-your-phone-cross-device-copy-paste/}}</ref>。

== 歷史 ==
2015年5月26日，微软宣布了{{link-en|Phone Companion}}应用，可将PC连接到[[Windows_Phone|Windows Phone]]、Android和[[IOS|IOS]][[智能手机|智能手机]]。 

在2018年5月7日举行的[[Build_(开发者大会)|Build 2018]]活动上，微软展示了Your Phone应用，用以替代先前發佈的{{link-en|Phone Companion}}，用户通過Your Phone可以在PC上查看手机中的近期照片，并发送短信<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.windowscentral.com/microsoft-announces-your-phone-windows-10-further-ties-your-smartphone-your-pc|title=New 'Your Phone' feature in Windows 10 further links your smartphone and PC|work=Windows Central|accessdate=2018-10-24|language=en|archive-date=2022-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220423133258/https://www.windowscentral.com/microsoft-announces-your-phone-windows-10-further-ties-your-smartphone-your-pc}}</ref>。 

在[[三星Galaxy_Note_10|三星Galaxy Note 10]]发布会上，微软公佈了 Your Phone附加功能，即用戶通过[[蓝牙|蓝牙]]可直接在PC上接听电话。该功能已于2020年2月20日向所有Android手机开放<ref>{{Cite web|title=Windows 10 Your Phone call support is now available for everyone|url=https://www.windowslatest.com/2020/02/02/windows-10-your-phone-app-call-support|accessdate=2020-02-08|author=|date=|first=|work=www.windowslatest.com|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20220107081835/https://www.windowslatest.com/2020/02/02/windows-10-your-phone-app-call-support/|archivedate=2022-01-07}}</ref>。 

